Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry, you resemble a girl I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a terrible pick up line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Christmas~ Christmas~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you well, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This insolent voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,None other than Kotobuki-sama for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I always thought you were a jinx.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I didn't think you'll look for me on your own. What a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am a nice guy to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right, on Christmas Eve morning the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We have an event as per custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're referring to a Christmas party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've spent quite long looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're looking for me because of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nice to just let loose and enjoy yourself once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's gonna be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Our Paranormal Investigation Association will have a show of hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Any news since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's been a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aren't you going to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She left on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why should I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't even know where to start looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(700,0)\pos(310,48)}http://wakusubs.wordpress.com
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome back, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome back? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You haven't been cleaning for the entire week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's fine. I will do my own cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't just barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry for giving you a wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait. You don't have to leave in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you saying? No one's misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The flowers are beautiful. Arigatou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Now where's the vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I just happen to find a perfect replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll add some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But the vase is filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How does Ruri stay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've been cooking and scaled myself slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It looks great, Ruri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's all thanks to you, Youko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can see the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You pickles! Are you trying to kill me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's Ruri Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's Ruri Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, I mean Ruri your sister... dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Can I call you by another name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right. Koruri. (Means Little Ruri)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Her attitude towards Youko and me is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You address Ruri Onee-chan. Are you her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think we can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's absolutely right. I'm her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Really? Then I hope you'll tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't even know what this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you mean by you don't wanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What a huge futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are not done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's fine, just let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She doesn't want to talk anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But where do I sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's somewhere you can sleep over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,See you at the party the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll leave Koruri-chan to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Did she go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well then, I'll take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Warm water is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,A bath has to be hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why are you in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I should be asking you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's there to be pain about, you pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Peeping on girls bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It wasn't on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I just stumbled onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You said you were bathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't think you can smoke your way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You said you were bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bathing in hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course. You bathe with hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That means you know how to adjust your body temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a Snow woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri didn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri... she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What about Ruri Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I only know I'm a Snow woman and my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Snow woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why am I a Snow woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why can't I touch humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why can't I touch someone I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why do you get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Leave Hiroshi-sama alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why? What happened? Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I have someone else in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Then Ruri subsequently disappeared that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama! Please embrace me, embrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Farewell, Hiroshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't go, Ruri. Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't go! Ruri! Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm going to look at society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,To understand the current world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why am I a Snow woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why can't I touch humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't even kiss someone I love most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi-sama, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What, it's only you, Koruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you want to date me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You tend to do incomprehensible stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's a Taimashi. (退魔師 Exorcist of sorts)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Taimashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They are beings that seeks to destroy us non-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She must have detected my aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Exterminate is... to kill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This must be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you know what she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She is a Snow woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But she's not an evil  existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please spare her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She didn't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because this is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's dark. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It wasn't intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Where's Koruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But she's really not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Though she can be quite the bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But she's not bad by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So please don't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll observe for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm Ayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I reside in the Miyama Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm Manabu Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'll be sure to notify you if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why do I have to sleep in the Kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What? Not asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Regarding Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You said she was unable to adjust her body temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, that's why Ruri was unable to touch anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She will scald herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So she bathes in cold water daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do you know it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You saw, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sorry, I did see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ruri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can gradually understand why Ruri chose to vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She seems to have taken a liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why leave when she's smitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How do you know she likes me anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because I think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Could you embrace me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's reasonable after how I bullied you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,are crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's too intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please be more gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, Koruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are we not attending the party together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You really OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Enjoy yourself. Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Merry Christmas! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Aoyama's special moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Right on, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nomura, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nomura's special moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Having fun, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,When are you going to stop being so indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You actually didn't want to come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, you shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got invited...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why won't you look for Ruri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You like her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She left on her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I don't have any reason to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How could you not understand Ruri-san's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Your feelings are what's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You like her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you can't understand her feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,just let your heart lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If you truly love her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,you should look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Living according to your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Didn't you use to be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's the reason I fell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Youko, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're too kind-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Making the guy you love ditch you on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's make immediate preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's gonna be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You can't bear to leave him on his own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We should go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ayaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I didn't mention to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's actually another Snow woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But she's..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She's a very precious woman to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You located Koruri because you managed to sense her aura, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.43,0:24:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I beg you, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The whereabouts of Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.01,0:24:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I believe you will know, Ayaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The foot of Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There's been an unbelievable aura at that place recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.06,0:24:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And it's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.44,0:25:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm going to find Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't look for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.44,0:25:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Koruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.63,0:25:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
